<br>
This State of Nature is simply every man for himself, whose only concerns are to keep himself alive while grabbing and holding onto as much as he can for as long as he can.  And because nature has made man basically equal in body and mind, man is in a constant state of 'Warre' to preserve his own life and his property (this includes wife and children).<br>
<br>
